<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Edit Spesies - InfoSea</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        #background-video {
            position: fixed;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            min-height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            object-fit: cover;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            z-index: -1;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #006994, #003366);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .header-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo-svg {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #66ccff;
        }

        main {
            margin-top: 80px;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 160px);
            padding: 2rem 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            color: white;
        }

        .edit-section {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .edit-form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .form-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .form-group label {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: white;
        }

        .form-control {
            padding: 0.8rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 5px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: white;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #66ccff;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        select.form-control {
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        select.form-control option {
            background: #003366;
            color: white;
        }

        textarea.form-control {
            min-height: 150px;
            resize: vertical;
        }

        .submit-btn {
            background: #006994;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .submit-btn:hover {
            background: #004d6d;
        }

        .back-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .back-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }

        footer {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #003366, #006994);
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        .footer-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .footer-section h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .footer-section p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .social-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        .social-links a:hover {
            color: #66ccff;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .bottom-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav ul {
                gap: 1rem;
            }

            .edit-section {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }

            .section-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .footer-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .social-links {
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <video autoplay muted loop id="background-video">
        <source src="/public/19016098-hd_1920_1080_30fps.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>

    <header>
        <div class="header-content">
            <a href="/" class="logo-container">
                <svg class="logo-svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M10,50 Q25,40 40,50 T70,50 T100,50" stroke="white" stroke-width="4" fill="none"/>
                    <path d="M10,65 Q25,55 40,65 T70,65 T100,65" stroke="white" stroke-width="4" fill="none"/>
                    <path d="M60,35 Q70,25 80,35 L85,30 L85,40 L80,35 Q70,45 60,35" fill="white"/>
                    <circle cx="30" cy="25" r="5" fill="white"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="logo-text">InfoSea</span>
            </a>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Beranda</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/species">Daftar Spesies</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/conservation">Area Konservasi</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/participation">Partisipasi</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/auth/login">Login</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="edit-section">
            <h1 class="section-title">Edit Spesies</h1>
            <form action="/species/edit/<%= species.id %>" method="POST" class="edit-form">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">Nama Spesies:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" value="<%= species.name %>" required class="form-control">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="status">Status:</label>
                    <select id="status" name="status" required class="form-control">
                        <option value="rentan" <%= species.status === 'rentan' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Rentan</option>
                        <option value="terancam" <%= species.status === 'terancam' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Terancam</option>
                        <option value="punah" <%= species.status === 'punah' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Punah</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="description">Deskripsi:</label>
                    <textarea id="description" name="description" class="form-control"><%= species.description %></textarea>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">
                    <i class="fas fa-save"></i> Perbarui Spesies
                </button>
            </form>
            <a href="/species" class="back-btn">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Kembali ke Daftar Spesies
            </a>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>Tentang InfoSea</h3>
                <p>InfoSea adalah platform edukasi yang didedikasikan untuk melestarikan dan mengedukasi masyarakat tentang kekayaan laut Indonesia.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>Kontak</h3>
                <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> info@infosea.id</p>
                <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> (021) 1234-5678</p>
                <p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Jakarta, Indonesia</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>Ikuti Kami</h3>
                <div class="social-links">
                    <a href="#" aria-label="Facebook"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" aria-label="Twitter"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" aria-label="YouTube"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" aria-label="LinkedIn"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bottom-footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 InfoSea. Dibuat Oleh Fadli Kurnia Ramadhan</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>